{"tid":89311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"研究表明：中國的肥胖人數超過了美國","createTime":"2017-01-21T09:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T12:51:10.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1add7d4d1f2c0fb1e5c355446d7f01cee90e483a","tid":89311,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:12:07.000Z","msg":"發表在醫學雜誌《柳葉刀》上的一項調查發現，全球成人肥胖者人數超過體重過輕的人數，而中國的男性肥胖人數為4320萬人，女性4640萬人，佔全球第一。<br />\n該項調查是由倫敦帝國理工大學的研究人員進行的。他們比較了從1975到2014年近2000萬成年男女的體質指數（BMI），得出的結果是男性肥胖總數增長了三倍，女性則翻了一番以上。<br />\n報告的作者警告，現在已經到了「嚴重肥胖疫情」的地步，並敦促各國政府採取行動。<br />\n英國公共衛生專家說，要想解決肥胖問題沒有單一的捷徑，它需要政府、有關行業、個人以及公眾的共同努力。<br />\n這項調查收集了186個國家成年人的數據，發現全球肥胖人數已經從1975年的一億零五百萬上升到2014年的六億四千一百萬。<br />\n而同時期的體重過輕的人數也在上升，從三億三千萬增長到四億六千兩百萬人。"},{"pid":"0e165b29c596bea6575a047cd53ce55ada4a9e35","tid":89311,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:16:13.000Z","msg":"但支那食唔飽嘅人無少過"},{"pid":"308ca1d0a4b401612e0ada8bb5b79da2ed31c7fa","tid":89311,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:22:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但支那食唔飽嘅人無少過</blockquote><br />\n朱門酒肉臭,路有凍死骨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca7d5066303dc941fd77e8be7015cafba8bead4","tid":89311,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:35:43.000Z","msg":"東亞胖夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f920d142028f6f0854ada42d1aaafe352f5947","tid":89311,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:44:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4cd7f53b9aab93b44a6c319b23eed4909d3b3a94","tid":89311,"uid":218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:52:13.000Z","msg":"懷仔"},{"pid":"c7593acc8d17db07bace0b99a5f86824bf3542c7","tid":89311,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T12:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a29c0188d0584d99c26b36d7b9541c9a631a746","tid":89311,"uid":67028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T12:05:56.000Z","msg":"如果要做比較<br />\n唔應該用人數 而係用比例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8574f4df08b4efbaba6ed69d13dff04f870ad8b","tid":89311,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T12:07:53.000Z","msg":"香港就亞洲最瘦，唔怪得毒撚多俾女人恰"},{"pid":"7a6798ce6a567b26d48caa6ccf4e86db891d4c3a","tid":89311,"uid":1508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T12:51:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果要做比較<br />\n唔應該用人數 而係用比例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跟共匪學架姐<br />\n佢地都好鍾意用總數黎吹奏自己架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}